      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 06:46:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TPG 和 GIC 拟斥资 75 亿美元收购电表制造商 Techem</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/tpg-gic-to-buy-energy-meter-maker-techem-in-7-5-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权公司 TPG Inc. 和新加坡主权财富基金 GIC Pte 同意从大股东 Partners Group Holding AG 手中收购德国能源计量公司 Techem GmbH，总对价约为 67 亿欧元（75 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/tpg-gic-to-buy-energy-meter-maker-techem-in-7-5-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 06:43:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼通胀率创三年新低，降息预期增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/indonesia-s-inflation-hits-three-year-low-boosts-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼消费者价格涨幅创近三年来新低，在食品和燃料成本下降且人们对消费需求低迷的担忧加剧的情况下，印尼央行本月可能会考虑进一步放松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/indonesia-s-inflation-hits-three-year-low-boosts-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 06:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典房东以三年来最快的速度出售债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/swedish-landlords-sell-bonds-at-the-fastest-pace-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率下降推动债券发行量激增，瑞典房东重返债券市场的数量达到了 2021 年繁荣时期以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/swedish-landlords-sell-bonds-at-the-fastest-pace-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Dreyfus 即将收购澳大利亚棉花生产商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/dreyfus-buys-almost-half-of-cotton-firm-closing-in-on-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳莫伊棉花有限公司 (Namoi Cotton Ltd.) 的独立董事建议股东接受路易达孚公司 (Louis Dreyfus Co.) 的最新收购要约，路易达孚公司当天早些时候提高了报价，并表示已收购了这家澳大利亚公司近一半的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/dreyfus-buys-almost-half-of-cotton-firm-closing-in-on-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 01:14:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔计划发行新日元债券以提振贸易公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/berkshire-plans-second-yen-bond-sale-in-2024-picks-underwriters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔哈撒韦公司计划今年第二次发行日元债券，因市场猜测该公司希望增加在日本的投资，这推动了贸易公司的股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/berkshire-plans-second-yen-bond-sale-in-2024-picks-underwriters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 01:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
